{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:0","text":"对每个 Tractor 应用程序的详细讨论。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:1","text":"tractor-engine"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:2","text":"用于手动启动 engine 的命令行工具。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:3","text":"tractor-blade"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:4","text":"用于手动启动 blade 的命令行工具。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:5","text":"Dashboard"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:6","text":"用于查询和控制作业与 blade 的基于浏览器的 GUI。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:7","text":"tractor-spool"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:8","text":"用于提交作业的命令行工具。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:9","text":"tq"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:10","text":"用于查询和控制作业与 blade 的强大命令行工具。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:11","text":"NIMBY"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:12","text":"用于管理本地主机参与调度情况的桌面 GUI。"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:13","text":"tractor-dbctl"}
{"item_id":"a66a92d20c:14","text":"用于管理后端数据库的命令行工具。"}
